trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the number of alternating <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.GroupItem"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir hvor loddrette <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.GroupItem"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: The AlternationCount property and the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.AlternationIndex%2A?displayProperty=fullName> attached property enable you to specify the appearance for two or more alternating <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupItem> objects.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen AlternationCount og <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.AlternationIndex%2A?displayProperty=fullName>vedlagte egenskapen gjør det mulig å angi utseendet for to eller flere alternative <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupItem>objekter.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupItem> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.AlternationIndex%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: For example, you can specify alternating background colors for every third <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupItem> in an <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl>.
trans-unit.target: Du kan for eksempel angi vekslende bakgrunnsfarge for hver tredje <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupItem>i en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupItem>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.AlternationIndex%2A?displayProperty=fullName> is assigned to each <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupItem> in the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.AlternationIndex%2A?displayProperty=fullName>Er tilordnet til hver enkelt <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupItem>i <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupItem> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.AlternationIndex%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.AlternationIndex%2A?displayProperty=fullName> begins at 0, increments until it is AlternationCount minus 1, and then restarts at 0.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.AlternationIndex%2A?displayProperty=fullName>starter ved 0 intervaller før det AlternationCount minus 1, og starter på 0.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.AlternationIndex%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: For example, if AlternationCount is 3 and there are seven <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupItem> objects in the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl>, the following table lists the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.AlternationIndex%2A?displayProperty=fullName> for each item.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel hvis AlternationCount er 3, og det er sju <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupItem>objekter i den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl>, følgende tabell lister av <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.AlternationIndex%2A?displayProperty=fullName>for hvert element.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.AlternationIndex%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupItem>

| Plasseringen av <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupItem>i <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl>|<xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.AlternationIndex%2A?displayProperty=fullName>| |-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------| |&1; |&0; | |&2; |&1; | |&3; |&2; | |&4; |&0; | |&5; |&1; | |&6; |&2; | |&7; |&0; | Det finnes flere metoder som du kan bruke til å angi forskjellig utseende for den alternative <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupItem>objekter.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupItem> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.AlternationIndex%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupItem>

trans-unit.source: One method is to bind properties in the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupStyle.HeaderTemplate%2A> or <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupStyle.ContainerStyle%2A> of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupStyle> to the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.AlternationIndex%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Én måte er binde egenskaper i <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupStyle.HeaderTemplate%2A>eller <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupStyle.ContainerStyle%2A>av den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupStyle>til <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.AlternationIndex%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.AlternationIndex%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupStyle> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupStyle.ContainerStyle%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupStyle.HeaderTemplate%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can then use an <xref:System.Windows.Controls.AlternationConverter> to specify which value should be applied to the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupItem> that has a certain <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.AlternationIndex%2A?displayProperty=fullName> value.
trans-unit.target: Deretter kan du bruke en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.AlternationConverter>til å angi hvilken verdi som skal brukes på den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupItem>som har en bestemt <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.AlternationIndex%2A?displayProperty=fullName>verdi.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.AlternationIndex%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupItem> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.AlternationConverter>

trans-unit.source: You can also use triggers to change the value of a property depending on the value of its <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.AlternationIndex%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Du kan også bruke utløsere til å endre verdien for egenskapen avhengig av verdien for den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.AlternationIndex%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.AlternationIndex%2A?displayProperty=fullName>
